thread.title: BRIEF-Cellnex FY Revenue Up 12 Pct At 792 Mln Euros YoY

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Cellnex FY Revenue Up 12 Pct At 792 Mln Euros YoY
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - CELLNEX TELECOM SA:
* FY REVENUE 792 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 707 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* FY ADJUSTED EBITDA 355 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 290 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* FY NET PROFIT 33 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 40 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* SEES 2018 OUTLOOK IMPLYING DOUBLE-DIGIT GROWTH IN KEY METRICS‍​
* SEES 2018 ADJUSTED EBITDA BETWEEN 405 MILLION EUROS - 415 MILLION EUROS
* SEES 2018 DIVIDENDS GROWTH OF 10 PERCENT Source text for Eikon:
Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
